<br>
Kanogan<br>
Magician 50th Season <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=iradin@themagicianstower>Iradin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#333333>(2/14/03 7:27:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=42.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How to Kill them without getting Aggro</span><hr size=1> I got my elemental maelstrom in thurg for 9pp off of a merchant.  Just lucky I guess.  My only attempt at Shardwurms was duoing with a necro friend at about level 45 and it ended badly when we pulled one as a bunch popped.  Resulted in my Gate colapsing and me shortly afterwards, and my damn necro friend feigning death.  We need that spell.<br>
